track.name: En Timme Kvar Att Leva
comments: to feel ur vibe is enough!

Brilliant mix of reggae and european folk, no wonder it's tagged "yann tiersen stoned". XD

Soothing, rocking and a bit melancholic, the perfect track for tired folks. ^^
The chords in combination with the 'piano ping' remind me of Manu Chao, which is no problem at all ;-)
i like the classical style, but too much sound in the end
